Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.38,0:01:32.74,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Trouble arises over\Nsuccession rights
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.78,0:01:35.34,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,in one of Soul Society’s high-ranking\Naristocratic families, the Kasumiohji Clan.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.58,0:01:39.38,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Their princess, Rurichiyo Kasumiohji,\Ntraveled to the World of the Living.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.67,0:01:43.85,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo reluctantly agrees\Nto become her bodyguard.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.85,0:01:47.58,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Rurichiyo, who is unaware that\Nher life is being targeted,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.58,0:01:51.26,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,turns Ichigo’s life upside down\Nwith her naive behavior.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.46,0:01:54.53,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,One day she runs away\Nfrom the house
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.54,0:01:59.38,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,over a trivial argument with\Nher stewards, Kenryu and Enryu,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.42,0:02:03.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,and encounters\Nan enemy assassin in town.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.53,0:02:08.27,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Orihime, who happened to be near,\Nmakes an attempt to fight him alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.54,0:02:11.97,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But Orihime and Rurichiyo are in\Ngreat danger against this assassin,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.97,0:02:13.47,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,who has a strange Zanpakuto.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.24,0:02:19.22,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Then Ichigo appears\Njust in time to save them.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.54,0:02:24.06,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo Kurosaki!\NIchigo Kurosaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.42,0:02:28.54,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it,\Nso early in the morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.96,0:02:29.53,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.26,0:02:32.65,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.65,0:02:33.97,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That doesn’t matter!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.38,0:02:36.97,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Lady Rurichiyo has\Ndisappeared again!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.30,0:02:49.21,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.54,0:02:52.42,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Is someone returning from\Nthe World of the Living?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.54,0:02:54.68,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,There’s no one here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.68,0:02:55.89,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,A malfunction?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.90,0:03:33.16,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Princess…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.82,0:03:36.63,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it’s you, Kumoi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.46,0:03:43.23,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.98,0:03:45.85,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! It’s the princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.70,0:03:49.67,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m glad to see you are well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.30,0:03:53.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Princess…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.91,0:03:58.12,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Where have you been all this time,\Nwithout telling me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.66,0:04:00.77,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I was with Kenryu and Enryu.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.77,0:04:03.82,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I do not need your permission\Nfor everything I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.32,0:04:06.03,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I beg to differ.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.86,0:04:08.66,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,If anything should happen to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.66,0:04:12.33,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,you are not the one\Nwho will be put to shame.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.86,0:04:16.42,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,The shame will be on\Nthe Kasumiohji Clan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.42,0:04:19.00,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Namely, your late\Nmother and father.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.01,0:04:22.47,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I know that without you telling me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.14,0:04:28.56,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you must behave like\Na princess of the Kasumiohji Clan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.10,0:04:30.25,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.02,0:04:42.19,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Oh yes, prepare my palanquin.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.02,0:04:45.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,And where are you off to this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.30,0:04:47.30,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,A tea ceremony!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.34,0:05:07.80,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you there, Hanza?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.70,0:05:12.22,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Sir Kumoi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.54,0:05:13.86,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,For some unknown reason,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.86,0:05:16.19,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,she has returned from\Nthe World of the Living.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.58,0:05:19.32,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Furthermore,\Nwithout Kenryu or Enryu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.66,0:05:21.18,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Do not let this opportunity pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.18,0:05:22.00,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.62,0:05:29.74,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Not again!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.14,0:05:32.94,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Be prepared.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.87,0:05:37.68,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.14,0:05:39.01,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What’s going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.74,0:05:42.62,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this? Stand back!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.74,0:05:44.50,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,– Yes sir!\N– Yes sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.66,0:05:47.94,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You should be aware\Nthat this Senkaimon
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.94,0:05:51.30,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,is used only by the princess\Nor the inspectors.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.46,0:05:53.46,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,B-But Sir Kenryu…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.98,0:05:58.14,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,The gate opened earlier\Nand no one was there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.46,0:06:04.04,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,So she went back after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.23,0:06:13.19,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I’m sorry. We can’t go to\NSoul Society through this gate.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.19,0:06:14.26,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There’s also a chance{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.26,0:06:17.86,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}that Miss Kasumiohji\Nwill return here before you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.30,0:06:20.99,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So we’ll keep a tight watch\Non this side.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.30,0:06:23.87,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Right. Thanks.\NI’m counting on you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.18,0:06:25.46,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We’ll be off.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.58,0:06:31.58,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Let’s hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.02,0:06:33.10,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,She probably snuck in
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.14,0:06:36.61,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,while the gatekeepers\Nweren’t paying attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.61,0:06:37.41,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.87,0:06:43.85,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys painstakingly find refuge\Nin the World of the Living
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.46,0:06:45.87,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,and she comes right back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.87,0:06:48.39,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,All your troubles were for nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.86,0:06:49.46,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Cripes…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.86,0:06:52.79,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s what you get for being\Ncaretakers of a spoiled princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.71,0:06:56.09,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What was that for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.14,0:06:58.06,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Talk!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.94,0:06:59.75,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,To be blunt,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.75,0:07:04.77,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,it is not the place of a low-life like you\Nto criticize the princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.95,0:07:09.77,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But it’s true that she’s spoiled.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.22,0:07:12.26,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What if she’s discovered by\Nthat guy named Kumoi,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.26,0:07:14.18,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,the very one\Nwho’s after her life?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.26,0:07:18.42,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You won’t get me a second time!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.02,0:07:22.02,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you do that for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.30,0:07:25.99,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You’re at fault for carelessly\Nsaying the name of the enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.62,0:07:30.89,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s her fault for wandering\Naround carelessly!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.89,0:07:36.00,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But, it stands that Lady Rurichiyo\Nis still a young child.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.18,0:07:37.47,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It can’t be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.38,0:07:42.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Let’s split up and search for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.48,0:07:44.30,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,We will search inside the mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.83,0:07:54.53,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn. Where did Rurichiyo go?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.02,0:07:57.05,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,She’ll get it when I find her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.54,0:08:01.34,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.90,0:08:04.10,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you in a hurry?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.14,0:08:09.42,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Long time no see!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.90,0:08:13.24,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Zaraki…\Nand Lieutenant Kusajishi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.54,0:08:15.74,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What’re you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.98,0:08:17.95,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh. That’s true.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.95,0:08:20.21,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Weren’t you in\Nthe World of the Living?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.46,0:08:21.26,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.90,0:08:22.83,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Um…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.82,0:08:24.68,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Err…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.38,0:08:27.15,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Is Ichigo here too?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.22,0:08:31.62,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Um…uh…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.82,0:08:47.04,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,So he’s here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.82,0:08:50.16,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup, he’s here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.16,0:08:52.79,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,And he’s pretty worked up\Nabout something.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.79,0:08:55.01,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup! He seems worked up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.34,0:08:58.34,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No… That’s…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.82,0:09:02.19,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,He’s here and hasn’t\Ncome to greet me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.50,0:09:06.16,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh well. I’ll go to him then.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.96,0:09:08.66,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,C-Captain Zaraki!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.73,0:09:14.46,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is bad. This thing\Nabout Ririchiyo is a secret.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.46,0:09:16.82,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I allow Ichigo and\NCaptain Zaraki to meet,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.82,0:09:18.64,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}things can get out of hand.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.34,0:09:24.08,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,She’s not on\Nthe castle grounds anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.70,0:09:27.97,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What’s the matter, Enryu?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.32,0:09:33.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.14,0:09:35.54,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It belongs to the princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.77,0:09:54.59,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,The door closed by itself!\NEnryu, where are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.62,0:09:56.47,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s too dark to see!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.66,0:09:58.22,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?! What?!\NSomething just touched me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.22,0:10:00.42,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay there for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.98,0:10:03.30,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Just until I get rid of the princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.58,0:10:13.12,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Princess, we have arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.62,0:10:21.50,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Lady Rurichiyo Kasumiohji\Nhas arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.14,0:10:39.12,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I thank you for your invitation today.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.14,0:10:43.29,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for coming so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.22,0:10:47.26,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You wait here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.38,0:10:48.18,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.54,0:10:52.46,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.46,0:10:56.63,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Why you…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.98,0:11:03.31,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You may leave us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.78,0:11:04.61,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,– Yes sir!\N– Yes sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.90,0:11:15.90,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ruricchi…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.90,0:11:19.29,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Sacchi…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.38,0:11:20.80,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,– It’s been so long!\N– It’s been so long!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.74,0:11:26.30,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on.\NEveryone is already here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.26,0:11:28.74,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It really has been so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.74,0:11:30.30,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.98,0:11:40.71,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, Ruricchi is here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.41,0:11:45.68,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,– Ruricchi, it’s been so long!\N– How have you been?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.06,0:11:49.39,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine. And how have you all been?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.42,0:11:52.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Ruricchi…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.66,0:11:58.53,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.22,0:12:10.71,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m so glad that you remembered.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.14,0:12:13.11,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,How could I forget?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.66,0:12:16.68,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It is proof of our friendship.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.34,0:12:31.42,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,There! Just a bit more, Enryu!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.42,0:12:33.71,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Good! We’re almost there!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.71,0:12:36.78,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,We won’t let Kumoi have his way!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.16,0:12:38.32,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! We can get through!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.48,0:12:41.32,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,We did it, Enryu!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.52,0:12:50.10,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,We’ll be right there,\NLady Rurichiyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.31,0:12:55.84,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I think she went in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.72,0:12:58.09,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.12,0:13:04.34,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey wait! I’m Substitute Soul Reaper,\NIchigo Kurosaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.44,0:13:08.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Rurichiyo went in there\Njust a while ago, didn’t she?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.12,0:13:10.62,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Substitute Soul Reaper?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.16,0:13:14.64,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you address\NLady Rurichiyo so casually!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.76,0:13:16.17,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You’re suspicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.00,0:13:22.81,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait! I’m a Substitute Soul Reaper\Nwho was asked by Kenryu…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.04,0:13:25.27,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You dare mention\NSir Kenryu’s name too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.27,0:13:27.79,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ve never heard of\Na Substitute Soul Reaper!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.84,0:13:31.65,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,He disappeared?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.65,0:13:33.46,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Where’d he go?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.96,0:13:38.56,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess “Substitute” Soul Reaper\Nain’t gonna work.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.56,0:13:40.08,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,There he is! Above the wall!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.08,0:13:41.17,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Oops!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.44,0:13:54.60,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ruricchi…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.04,0:14:00.11,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,This was made with the year’s\Nfirst batch of tea leaves.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.64,0:14:01.87,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.56,0:14:15.33,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck?\NHow filthy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.48,0:14:19.04,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I-Ichigo!\NWhat are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.44,0:14:22.21,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s my line!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.40,0:14:24.60,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Coming here on a whim…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.08,0:14:28.15,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, let’s go back.\NEveryone’s waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.00,0:14:31.51,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn’t have\Nfollowed me here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.51,0:14:33.70,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,This is an important tea ceremony!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.40,0:14:37.06,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Rurichiyo, quit acting so spoiled.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.76,0:14:41.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What’s this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.66,0:14:43.22,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What’s going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.56,0:14:44.97,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I beg your pardon, Princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.48,0:14:47.88,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,A message was brought by\Na vassal of the Kasumiohji Clan
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.88,0:14:50.31,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,that a robber had\Ninfiltrated the grounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.16,0:14:55.21,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait! I’m not a suspicious guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.44,0:14:56.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Rurichiyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.37,0:15:00.05,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I don’t know this man.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.60,0:15:03.31,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ruricchi! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.52,0:15:05.00,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Rurichiyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.72,0:15:07.89,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.60,0:15:10.96,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,– He disappeared!\N– Where’d he go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.96,0:15:11.92,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Find him!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.84,0:15:13.96,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That way!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.56,0:15:30.55,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m in no mood to enjoy the tea ceremony\Nnow that Ichigo appeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.24,0:15:44.42,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What’s wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.92,0:15:49.69,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you the child of\None of the servants?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.88,0:15:52.88,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Did your mother scold you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.40,0:15:54.60,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Now come.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.40,0:16:03.91,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there something over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.36,0:16:16.98,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What about this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.52,0:16:53.42,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.24,0:17:02.27,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.45,0:17:05.24,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Rurichiyo! Are you all right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.28,0:17:10.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Rather… Who is she?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.03,0:17:20.12,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.12,0:17:21.06,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,There he is!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.89,0:17:24.60,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Lady Rurichiyo is in danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.60,0:17:27.27,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you point your blade\Nat a helpless child!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.04,0:17:29.12,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,No, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.12,0:17:29.95,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,This is…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.84,0:17:31.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.60,0:17:33.10,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on, you see…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.96,0:17:36.97,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a minute!\NThat kid is the…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.56,0:17:42.24,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Princess Rurichiyo, are you hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.68,0:17:44.84,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.80,0:18:00.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.32,0:18:18.32,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Kenpachi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.48,0:18:21.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,So, Ichigo…\NYou’re here, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.48,0:18:23.21,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yoo-hoo! Itchy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.40,0:18:26.68,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,C-Captain Zaraki of Squad 11!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.46,0:18:48.61,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Zaraki!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.69,0:18:54.32,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo… What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.83,0:18:59.64,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, Lady Rurichiyo,\Nplease get in.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.80,0:19:11.43,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Please don’t scold Rurichiyo.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.73,0:19:19.10,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Umm…I’m going to\Nbe wed shortly.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.50,0:19:21.30,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh, that’s great news.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.66,0:19:22.52,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.52,0:19:24.11,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She doesn’t even love him.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.11,0:19:29.23,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She’s being forced to marry\Nsomeone she’s never met!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.16,0:19:36.08,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It’s a marriage that was sealed\Nbetween two noble families{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.08,0:19:37.22,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}since they were children.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.27,0:19:41.88,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don’t look like that.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.40,0:19:45.32,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I plan to accept it as part of my fate.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.10,0:19:49.24,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So this is my final tea ceremony.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.53,0:19:51.68,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ruricchi knew that,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.68,0:19:54.50,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}so she went through great pains\Nto come and see me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.22,0:19:58.80,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Because we may never\Nbe able to meet again.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.22,0:20:03.41,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You must be marrying\Ninto a very strict family.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.12,0:20:04.92,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yes.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.84,0:20:12.92,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh my… How strange.\NIt’s not as though I’m sad.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.32,0:20:17.32,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sacchi…{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.59,0:20:24.12,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess aristocratic families\Nhave no freedom.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.96,0:20:26.00,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Without a doubt,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.04,0:20:29.26,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,it’s a totally different place\Nfrom the World of the Living.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.08,0:20:35.25,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Zaraki…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.58,0:20:38.31,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Due to certain circumstances,\Nwe are working under secrecy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.81,0:20:43.22,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,May I ask you to keep this incident\Nto yourself for now?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.63,0:20:45.88,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I don’t know what your reason is,\Nand besides,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.88,0:20:50.24,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m too busy to remember\Nwhat’s what.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.17,0:20:54.76,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Kenny, you’re not too smart.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.46,0:20:57.68,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.36,0:21:01.20,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I was amused today.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.47,0:21:05.01,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring Ichigo back again.\NI’ll wear him ragged.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.24,0:21:07.24,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ragged, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.83,0:21:09.52,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ragged?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.25,0:21:12.08,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,See ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.63,0:21:17.92,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.35,0:21:21.80,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,We’re going back as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.00,0:21:23.80,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.84,0:21:31.84,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What’re you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.49,0:21:33.28,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.08,0:21:43.55,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,He didn’t even quiver when\Nhe felt my Spiritual Pressure.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.36,0:21:47.12,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Seems like an interesting fellow.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.11,0:23:21.51,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That Kenpachi…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.51,0:23:24.21,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if he’s really gonna\Nkeep the secret about us.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.21,0:23:25.42,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.42,0:23:27.03,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Kenny always says\Nit’s too much of a bother
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.03,0:23:28.97,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,and he never reports a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.97,0:23:32.09,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Then who’s been preparing\Nthe Squad 11 reports?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.09,0:23:33.03,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I dunno.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.03,0:23:34.53,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.18,0:23:36.54,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Illustrated Guide to Soul Reapers!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.64,0:23:44.15,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.15,0:23:47.07,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Baldy made this scooter\Nfor my birthday!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.27,0:23:49.43,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you in my mansion?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.43,0:23:51.07,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Because it’s so big!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.26,0:23:54.08,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I guess it's useless\Nto tell her to stop.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.62,0:23:58.08,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Madam Chairman,\Nit’s time for tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.20,0:24:00.45,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, what’s the snack today?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.45,0:24:02.32,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,The Madam Chairman\Nhas confetti candy.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.58,0:24:04.15,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!